@AvailableSince("0.0.5") public class KyoriInstrumentManagerImpl extends Object implements io.github.idankoblik.jukebox.manager.InstrumentManager<net.kyori.adventure.key.Key>
The implementation of the InstrumentManager that manages a collection of instruments associated with their respective byte identifiers and the corresponding sound keys.
